.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146a3e6b74995c2761b8012aecd76dcf1e13e362","tid":1535533,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"隨時中共都唔知有呢一著, 度左大半日都諗唔到點拆, 唯有鳩流流交份半炒車稿"},{"pid":"c323e2b301f4cfc50497da1f221ed02d8dca7cf5","tid":1535533,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"捉蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}